de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.algorithm.clustering.em

Class DiagonalGaussianModelFactory<V extends NumberVector>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.algorithm.clustering.em.AbstractEMModelFactory<V,EMModel>
      • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.algorithm.clustering.em.DiagonalGaussianModelFactory<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - vector type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    EMClusterModelFactory<V,EMModel>

    public class DiagonalGaussianModelFactory<V extends NumberVector>
extends AbstractEMModelFactory<V,EMModel>
    Factory for EM with multivariate gaussian models using diagonal matrixes. These models have individual variances, but no covariance, so this corresponds to the 'VVI' model in Mclust (R).
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
